| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2181 — Recovery Inhibition (cactus)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2ee46c5b-6c32-5bf7-bb46-f66409f291d8"
